WEBVTT

00:00:01.116 --> 00:00:02.568
I’m a bald man --

00:00:02.568 --> 00:00:03.635
(Laughter)

00:00:03.635 --> 00:00:05.037
but I don’t miss my hair.

00:00:06.054 --> 00:00:09.041
What I do miss
is going to the hairdresser.

00:00:10.092 --> 00:00:14.279
I found it to be such an enjoyable
and relaxing experience.

00:00:14.947 --> 00:00:17.916
I loved it when they would
rub their fingers through my hair

00:00:17.916 --> 00:00:19.718
while they washed
my hair in the sink.

00:00:20.252 --> 00:00:22.654
I enjoyed it when
they walked me over to the chair,

00:00:22.654 --> 00:00:24.423
and they would play with my hair more

00:00:24.423 --> 00:00:27.609
and talk to me about different hairstyles
and haircuts I could get.

00:00:27.876 --> 00:00:31.547
And I even enjoyed
the gentle sound of the scissors --